      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im planning a trip to chicago soon and i'll be staying by myself. i'm looking for a spot that feels pretty safe, upscale, and has a nice community vibe... like somewhere i won't have to worry about much. given the current social climate, are there any specific neighborhoods i should avoid to make sure i don't run into any trouble?",
